<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Brutish" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Brutish,</orth> bestial: <cit><quote>wouldst gabble like a thing most b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.357" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 357</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as sensual as the b. sting itself,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.7.66" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 7, 66</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>b. wrath,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 2.1.118" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 1, 118</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>O judgment, thou art fled to b. beasts,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 3.2.110" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. III, 2, 110</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>unnatural, detested, b. villain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 1.2.82" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 2, 82</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>